## Installation

### Add Helm repository

```shell
helm repo add evtechteam https://evtechteam.github.io/helm-charts
helm repo update
```

## Install Node-RED GitOps chart

Using default config:

```bash
helm install --generate-name evtechteam/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

